amily: Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; font-size: 11pt\">&nbsp;\n    </FONT></td></tr>\n</table>\n<P STYLE=\"font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 9.75pt 0; text-indent: 0\">&nbsp;</P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0\"><FONT STYLE=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; font-size: 11pt\">For\nfurther information, please contact:</FONT></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0\"><FONT STYLE=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; font-size: 11pt\">&nbsp;</FONT></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0\"><FONT STYLE=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; font-size: 11pt\">Patrick\nDrouin</FONT></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0\"><FONT STYLE=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; font-size: 11pt\">Senior\nVice President, Investor Relations</FONT></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0\"><FONT STYLE=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; font-size: 11pt\">Silver\nWheaton Corp.</FONT></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0\"><FONT STYLE=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; font-size: 11pt\">Tel:\n1-844-288-9878</FONT></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 11pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 0\"><FONT STYLE=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; font-size: 11pt\">Email:\n<FONT STYLE=\"color: Blue\"><U>info@silverwheaton.com</U></FONT></FONT></P>\n\n\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 9.75pt 0; text-indent: 0\"><FONT STYLE=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; font-size: 11pt\">&nbsp;</FONT></P>\n\n<P STYLE=\"font: 10pt Arial, Helvetica, Sans-Serif; margin: 9.75pt 0\"></P>\n\n</BODY>\n</HTML>\n</TEXT>\n</DOCUMENT>\n"
